{"TopicId":188979,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.12.x] Improved \u0026amp; Updated Chase Camera","CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T13:21:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T13:21:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOriginally written by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/72433-bahamutod/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002272433\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/72433-bahamutod/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@BahamutoD\u003C/a\u003E, then maintained by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/10788-papa_joe/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002210788\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/10788-papa_joe/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Papa_Joe\u003C/a\u003E, this mod has been abandoned for too long, so I\u0027m adopting it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOriginal thread here:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/72457-11-improved-chase-camera-v16-apr-23/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/72457-11-improved-chase-camera-v16-apr-23/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPrevious thread here:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/173436-14x-improved-chase-camera-v1621-apr-13-2018/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/173436-14x-improved-chase-camera-v1621-apr-13-2018/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EAvailability\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nDownload:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/2249/Improved%20and%20Updated%20Chase%20Camera\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/2249/Improved and Updated Chase Camera\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSource:\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ImprovedChaseCamera/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ImprovedChaseCamera/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLicense:\u00A0 GPLv3\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWhat is Improved Chase Camera?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nThis plugin gives you the option to make the camera follow your surface velocity vector.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nThis gives you a better feeling on how your plane is moving, its angle of attack, sideslip, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nPress\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETab\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Eto toggle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n(You can change the key in settings.cfg).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nToggling it off and on will bring it back to the default view angle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nSet autoSnap to true in the config to have it always snap back to default angle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nThe default view angle can be changed in the config file as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nTwo modes:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n1. Toggle while in\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELocked\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Emode: Camera rolls with plane.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n2. Toggle while in\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFree\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Emode: Camera stays level.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nChase mode:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/azPHpQvR4rY?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFree chase mode:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/ofhKWrh8hZw?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Beetlecat","CreatedById":92207,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-17T19:42:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe return of the best camera. TY! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KraterKreator","CreatedById":150238,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-19T00:50:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022129964\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/129964-linuxgurugamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@linuxgurugamer\u003C/a\u003E! My hero! Thank you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-12T01:22:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew release, 1.6.4\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nUpdated for KSP 1.8\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darth_diamond","CreatedById":206754,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-12T22:31:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, i know its been a while, but could you make a mode where the camera chases the cursor when using mouse aim flight?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-12T22:39:52Z\u0022 title=\u002208/12/2020 10:39  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 12, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Darth_diamond\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Krazy1","CreatedById":203523,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-25T05:53:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWorks for me in 1.11.2. Much better than stock. Also recommend \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/175359-19x-afbw-revived-joystick-controller-mod/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EAFBW\u003C/a\u003E for joystick calibration.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sub31","CreatedById":211491,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-05T19:44:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, for some reason the mod is being very finicky. I managed to get it working once, but only for a single flight. I\u0027m not sure what\u0027s happening here.\u00A0 In ksp.log, the mod doesn\u0027t throw any errors, and configs load fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-06T21:58:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223966957\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620243853\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sub31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/5/2021 at 3:44 PM, Sub31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, for some reason the mod is being very finicky. I managed to get it working once, but only for a single flight. I\u0027m not sure what\u0027s happening here.\u00A0 In ksp.log, the mod doesn\u0027t throw any errors, and configs load fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou are hitting tab?\u00A0 It changes the way it works depending on when you activate it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sub31","CreatedById":211491,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-07T15:59:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I am. The dialog\u00A0 saying the camera improvement was activated showed up once for me, but only ever during one flight.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nOther mods are Mouse Aim Flight, Planetshine, Waterfall, Restock, Restock\u002B. Logs don\u0027t contain any errors thrown by the mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-07T16:53:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223968245\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620403198\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sub31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n53 minutes ago, Sub31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I am. The dialog\u00A0 saying the camera improvement was activated showed up once for me, but only ever during one flight.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nOther mods are Mouse Aim Flight, Planetshine, Waterfall, Restock, Restock\u002B. Logs don\u0027t contain any errors thrown by the mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout any logs, I can\u0027t say anything else\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sub31","CreatedById":211491,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-07T18:18:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223967835\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620338305\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou are hitting tab?\u00A0 It changes the way it works depending on when you activate it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223968316\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620406416\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout any logs, I can\u0027t say anything else\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.mediafire.com/file/d3qdy9yn8n80hkb/Player.log/file\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.mediafire.com/file/d3qdy9yn8n80hkb/Player.log/file\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLink to player.log.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-07T19:16:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstall ZeroMiniAVC to automatically remove all\u00A0 the MiniAVC.dll files that you have, then try again\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sub31","CreatedById":211491,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-07T23:23:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.mediafire.com/file/pok6n6o3mrf3vp4/copyPlayer.log/file\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.mediafire.com/file/pok6n6o3mrf3vp4/copyPlayer.log/file\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nHere is a newer log.\u00A0 Still not turning on when keybind pressed. (I have set to L as primary and Tab as secondary)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-13T16:36:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223968581\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620429834\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sub31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/7/2021 at 7:23 PM, Sub31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.mediafire.com/file/pok6n6o3mrf3vp4/copyPlayer.log/file\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.mediafire.com/file/pok6n6o3mrf3vp4/copyPlayer.log/file\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nHere is a newer log.\u00A0 Still not turning on when keybind pressed. (I have set to L as primary and Tab as secondary)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat log only gets to the main menu, please get in flight and try that, then post the log\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stk2008","CreatedById":162264,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-13T16:58:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223968581\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620429834\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sub31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/8/2021 at 12:23 AM, Sub31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.mediafire.com/file/pok6n6o3mrf3vp4/copyPlayer.log/file\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.mediafire.com/file/pok6n6o3mrf3vp4/copyPlayer.log/file\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nHere is a newer log.\u00A0 Still not turning on when keybind pressed. (I have set to L as primary and Tab as secondary)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou also must press v once to get intio free camera mode then press tab.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found it does not work if you get on runway then just press tab which I think the camera is defaulted to auto it must be in one of the other modes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso recap get on runway press v and get into free mode you will see it say so at top middle of screen then press tab take off it should centre on rear of craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"alberro\u002B","CreatedById":199496,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-13T18:46:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI gotta get this, it\u0027s honestly exactly what I wanted the Chase camera to be all this time. Thank you!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003Ealso, reminds me of ace combat zero\u0027s camera\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sub31","CreatedById":211491,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-13T20:36:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223971681\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620923805\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat log only gets to the main menu, please get in flight and try that, then post the log\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry! I found out just now that the hotkey only functions when you are in locked or free cam. Sorry for wasting your time. Pretty embarassing haha\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-14T18:39:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223971836\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221620938187\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Sub31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, Sub31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry! I found out just now that the hotkey only functions when you are in locked or free cam. Sorry for wasting your time. Pretty embarassing haha\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBelieve it or not, took me a while to figure it out also, even after I had adopted it.\u00A0 Glad you got it figured out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stk2008","CreatedById":162264,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-15T10:03:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep thats what my comment above was about again I to was like oh its not working \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-29T00:54:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew release, 1.6.4.1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRenamed DLL for \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E compatibility\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAdded AssemblyFileVersion\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nUpdated version file for 1.12\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-26T22:54:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew release, 1.6.4.2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nChanged Update to FixedUpdate (slight optimization)\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astra Infinitum","CreatedById":221662,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-05T19:30:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223688742\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571318508\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022linuxgurugamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/17/2019 at 8:21 AM, linuxgurugamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOriginally written by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/72433-bahamutod/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002272433\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/72433-bahamutod/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@BahamutoD\u003C/a\u003E, then maintained by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/10788-papa_joe/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002210788\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/10788-papa_joe/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Papa_Joe\u003C/a\u003E, this mod has been abandoned for too long, so I\u0027m adopting it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOriginal thread here:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/72457-11-improved-chase-camera-v16-apr-23/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/72457-11-improved-chase-camera-v16-apr-23/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPrevious thread here:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/173436-14x-improved-chase-camera-v1621-apr-13-2018/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/173436-14x-improved-chase-camera-v1621-apr-13-2018/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EAvailability\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nDownload:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/2249/Improved%20and%20Updated%20Chase%20Camera\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/2249/Improved and Updated Chase Camera\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSource:\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ImprovedChaseCamera/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ImprovedChaseCamera/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLicense:\u00A0 GPLv3\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWhat is Improved Chase Camera?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nThis plugin gives you the option to make the camera follow your surface velocity vector.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nThis gives you a better feeling on how your plane is moving, its angle of attack, sideslip, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nPress\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETab\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Eto toggle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n(You can change the key in settings.cfg).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nToggling it off and on will bring it back to the default view angle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nSet autoSnap to true in the config to have it always snap back to default angle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nThe default view angle can be changed in the config file as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nTwo modes:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n1. Toggle while in\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELocked\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Emode: Camera rolls with plane.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n2. Toggle while in\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFree\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Emode: Camera stays level.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nChase mode:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/azPHpQvR4rY?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFree chase mode:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/ofhKWrh8hZw?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat would i put in the setting.cfg for \u0022primary =\u0022 if i wanted the keystroke toggle to be \u003Cstrong\u003EControl\u002B numpad 1 \u003C/strong\u003E?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nprimary = ______________ ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-08-05T19:47:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is what\u0027s there:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E    ENABLE_CHASE\n    {\n        primary = Tab\n        secondary = None\n        group = 0\n        switchState = Any\n    }\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can try the following:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EKeypad1\nKeypad_1\nKeypadOne\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI listed them in order of what I think is most likely to work\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SafetyDancer","CreatedById":201940,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-01T14:25:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s no \u0022Issues\u0022 page on the github so I\u0027ll leave this here: Tab takes a lot of presses before Improved Camera turns on. The snapback is also borked because it just hard-prevents me from adjusting my camera. Once activated, it does work as advertised.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-02T02:58:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224267965\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188979\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680359130\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022201940\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SafetyDancer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, SafetyDancer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s no \u0022Issues\u0022 page on the github so I\u0027ll leave this here: Tab takes a lot of presses before Improved Camera turns on. The snapback is also borked because it just hard-prevents me from adjusting my camera. Once activated, it does work as advertised.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo logs, no support.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}